"""
qrecall — Find similar prior questions and lazily load their knowledge.

Commands:
  qrecall "query"                      Search for similar prior sessions
  qrecall show <session_id_prefix>     Lazy-load knowledge from a match
  qrecall backfill                     Embed all sessions with summaries but no embeddings
"""

